      "text": "ハクロニム",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1782275600,
      "updated": 1782275600
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3b5de20000000000d6e212",
      "text": " 造語法の一つを表す私の[造語][hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1782275600,
      "updated": 1782276320
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3b5deb0000000000d6e214",
      "text": "  英：hackronym",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1782275609,
      "updated": 1782275617
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3b5df70000000000d6e215",
      "text": "  [アクロニム]と[イニシャリズム]を組み合わせて読む頭字語",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1782275621,
      "updated": 1782276315
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3b5e0a0000000000d6e216",
      "text": "  アクロニムを叩き割り、上手く組み合わせたようなところから「ハック」",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1782275640,
      "updated": 1782275657
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3b5e210000000000d6e217",
      "text": "  [SLFS]（s-L-fs、ス-エル-フス→セルフス）、[KUST]（ku-S-t、ク-エス-ト、クエスト）など[希哲館]用語にしばしば見られる",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1782275663,
      "updated": 1782275802
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3b5ead0000000000d6e218",
      "text": "  有名な例では [Qt] が近い",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1782275802,
      "updated": 1782276377
    },
